title: RV Lot For Rent
posting_body: Small but well-treed RV lot available for rent in the Tejas Mobile Plaza located on Highway 71 just west of the airport.
The lot rents for $615/month and water and electricity are included in this price.
Before the application process can begin, you will have to submit a photograph of your RV for approval before the
background check and credit check can begin.
Please call 830.632.562 seven for more information.
